1
00:00:14,840 --> 00:00:18,404
♪I intentionally bump into you
and test you by teasing you♪

2
00:00:18,840 --> 00:00:22,480
♪Your fingertips
are beating the drumbeat of my heart♪

3
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:26,080
♪Your teasing eyes on my lips♪

4
00:00:26,738 --> 00:00:28,904
♪What a game of extreme flirting♪

5
00:00:29,966 --> 00:00:32,475
♪I play along with you,
pulling and teasing♪

6
00:00:32,595 --> 00:00:34,335
♪Your wrist brushing past my waist♪

7
00:00:34,486 --> 00:00:36,280
♪A force that is too intense♪

8
00:00:36,584 --> 00:00:38,480
♪A prelude that is too ambiguous♪

9
00:00:38,720 --> 00:00:40,341
♪Your eyes are invading my lips♪

10
00:00:40,680 --> 00:00:44,480
♪The breathing gradually
becomes mysterious♪

11
00:00:45,707 --> 00:00:48,520
♪Crossing the red lines one by one♪

12
00:00:49,200 --> 00:00:50,960
♪No more resisting love♪

13
00:00:54,430 --> 00:00:56,339
[Indulgence]

14
00:00:56,363 --> 00:00:59,920
[Based on fanqienovel.com's work
'Desire to Flirt' by Red Hat]

15
00:01:01,617 --> 00:01:03,721
[Episode 5]

16
00:01:07,080 --> 00:01:08,120
Dr. Bai!

17
00:01:08,280 --> 00:01:08,800
Dr. Bai!

18
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:10,840
Why haven't you been answering my calls?

19
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:11,800
You don't even reply to my messages.

20
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:14,720
I don't know you.

21
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:15,840
That's not possible.

22
00:01:16,240 --> 00:01:17,560
When I was sick and hospitalized,

23
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:18,800
you took care of me all the time.

24
00:01:18,800 --> 00:01:19,920
You must love me, right?

25
00:01:20,360 --> 00:01:21,400
You still love me.

26
00:01:22,080 --> 00:01:23,080
I do that with all my patients.

27
00:01:23,080 --> 00:01:24,160
That's not true.

28
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:25,280
You must love me.

29
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:34,600
Who are you?

30
00:01:35,600 --> 00:01:36,840
She's a former patient.

31
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:38,560
We know each other.

32
00:01:38,720 --> 00:01:39,680
He loves me.

33
00:01:39,880 --> 00:01:41,440
Look, I even have photos.

34
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:42,400
Miss,

35
00:01:42,720 --> 00:01:43,920
it's against the law to slander someone

36
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:45,440
and stalk them.

37
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:47,800
I'll have to call the police

38
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,680
if you keep this up.

39
00:01:49,880 --> 00:01:51,040
You're a bad woman!

40
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:52,360
I won't let you get away with this!

41
00:02:03,320 --> 00:02:03,960
Here you go.

42
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:10,600
Get changed.

43
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,520
You're quite something,

44
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:27,880
having stalking fans

45
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,240
even as a doctor.

46
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:38,560
Why did you help me?

47
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:42,360
Isn't it only natural for a big sister
to help her little brother?

48
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:43,680
Besides,

49
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:46,040
I've always hated bullies
since I was a kid.

50
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,880
Have you always stood up
for others like this?

51
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:51,360
Were you in an orphanage
when you were a child?

52
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,160
No.

53
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:53,960
Stop asking.

54
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:56,520
Let me hear

55
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:57,800
if what you're saying

56
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,400
is true.

57
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:15,720
This is where

58
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:16,720
the heart is.

59
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,160
Did you hear anything?

60
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:24,200
You're in good health.

61
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:32,960
So,

62
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:35,240
do you want to continue?

63
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,320
I have a gathering

64
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,480
tonight.

65
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:49,040
I don't have time for this.

66
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:01,000
I wouldn't have known
if Xu Wei hadn't told me.

67
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,240
That scumbag Zhao Yibin.

68
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,280
He begged me

69
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:06,320
to give him some business

70
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:08,240
because he said he would
take care of Zhao Quanyou.

71
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:09,840
Turns out,

72
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:12,560
he didn't care at all
about Zhao Quanyou's family.

73
00:04:13,279 --> 00:04:13,719
Kick him out

74
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:15,560
of the service providers immediately.

75
00:04:15,959 --> 00:04:17,199
Cut off all business ties.

76
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:18,560
Yes, sir.

77
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,160
Are you all right?

78
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:57,520
Are you hurt?

79
00:04:59,960 --> 00:05:00,680
I'm fine.

80
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:01,840
It's just a minor injury.

81
00:05:02,280 --> 00:05:02,840
Nothing serious.

82
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,440
I didn't know you had it in you.

83
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:10,080
I used to practice Taekwondo.

84
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,160
How can you still be making jokes

85
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:13,520
when you're injured?

86
00:05:13,520 --> 00:05:14,200
Take off your shirt.

87
00:05:21,440 --> 00:05:22,240
Does it hurt?

88
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:23,960
Just a blunt force injury.

89
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:24,960
Nothing serious.

90
00:05:52,840 --> 00:05:53,760
I'll be gentle.

91
00:05:55,840 --> 00:05:56,640
What's wrong?

92
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,200
Since you've been around,

93
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:04,280
I've gained injuries one after another.

94
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,240
First, my arm, and now, my back.

95
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:08,760
Done.

96
00:06:12,440 --> 00:06:13,800
Thank you for saving me.

97
00:06:15,080 --> 00:06:16,400
I was scared.

98
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:19,720
You were worried about me.

99
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:22,120
You got hurt because of me.

100
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:25,480
It's natural for a big sister
to be concerned.

101
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:27,720
You don't have to pretend

102
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:29,120
to be an older sister in front of me.

103
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:31,000
Well, it's not like
I can be your younger sister.

104
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,760
I'm not in the habit
of pretending to be young.

105
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:34,040
Get some rest.

106
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,120
Good night.

107
00:06:36,760 --> 00:06:37,320
Xu Wei,

108
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,400
have you crossed someone recently?

109
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:43,840
Don't worry about it.

110
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:45,600
I know who it is.

111
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:05,480
Hey, Ms. Xu,
come to the old house tomorrow.

112
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:12,760
What are you doing?

113
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:16,800
Who are you?

114
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,440
Why do you have the key to our house?

115
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:19,640
Your house?

116
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:21,120
This is my house.

117
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:23,840
My father transferred the house
to me a long time ago.

118
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:25,880
I need money urgently,

119
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,120
so I'm selling the house.

120
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,360
In that case,

121
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,080
why not sell it to me?

122
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,160
Sure.

123
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:32,840
I want three million in full.

124
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:34,840
Three million?

125
00:07:35,840 --> 00:07:38,040
Is this old house worth that much?

126
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:40,000
I decide how much it's worth.

127
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:41,160
If you want to buy it,

128
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:42,600
give me the full payment by tomorrow.

129
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:43,960
If not, get lost.

130
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,960
Mr. Landlord?

131
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:51,480
It's Xu Wei.

132
00:07:52,160 --> 00:07:53,320
Your son said
you were selling the house.

133
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:54,960
What's going on?

134
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:58,480
Daddy Bai,

135
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:01,280
you have to give my drawing to Mommy Xu.

136
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:04,400
Senior,

137
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,480
the operation is starting soon.

138
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,160
I'll head over first.

139
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:06,560
Okay.

140
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:26,320
What's the matter?

141
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:27,480
Dad.

142
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,040
Xu Wei...

143
00:08:42,413 --> 00:08:43,413
[Cheque]

144
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,240
What are you doing in my room?

145
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:58,760
What is this?

146
00:09:08,220 --> 00:09:12,724
♪Hidden clouds,
dim light falling on the back♪

147
00:09:14,115 --> 00:09:21,844
♪The solitary bench at the street corner
shelters emotions♪

148
00:09:24,084 --> 00:09:27,644
♪The moon's trajectory in the night sky♪

149
00:09:28,204 --> 00:09:31,725
♪Is mending my sad heart♪

150
00:09:32,045 --> 00:09:34,524
♪My courage to get close to you♪

151
00:09:34,974 --> 00:09:38,181
♪Stops me from running away♪

152
00:09:39,364 --> 00:09:41,284
♪The wheel of fate is turning,
and we meet again♪

153
00:09:41,575 --> 00:09:43,028
♪Piecing our memories desperately♪

154
00:09:43,484 --> 00:09:45,724
♪Love takes us by surprise♪

155
00:09:46,524 --> 00:09:48,244
♪The you in the photo album♪

156
00:09:48,684 --> 00:09:52,844
♪Are shining in the past like stars♪

157
00:09:54,259 --> 00:09:57,364
♪You are in the light and shadow♪

158
00:09:58,044 --> 00:10:01,524
♪Melting all my fear away♪

159
00:10:01,884 --> 00:10:05,378
♪Those youthful memories
are healing enough♪

160
00:10:05,828 --> 00:10:09,644
♪That I become obsessed with them♪

161
00:10:10,044 --> 00:10:13,524
♪The world is suddenly full of meanings♪

162
00:10:14,101 --> 00:10:17,724
♪Walking through the rain,
I have found you♪

163
00:10:18,724 --> 00:10:20,364
♪In between the embrace♪

164
00:10:20,724 --> 00:10:23,644
♪Are the stars
scattered across the horizon♪
